'''Katherine Dickinson''' (also known as '''Kathy Howsen'''; born 1952) is an American mailwoman. She is the ex-wife of restaurater [[Donald Howsen (V2)|Donald Howsen]], brother of football player [[Derek Howsen (V2)|Derek Howsen]]. 

==Early life==

==Career==
Dickinson first started working as a mailwoman in 1970. 

... 

After delivering mail for over forty years, Dickinson retired in 2017.

==Personal life==
Kathy married Donald in 1973. They had four children together before divorcing in 1982: 
* Daniella (born 1975) 
* Abigail ("Abby"; born 1976) 
* Bailey (born 1977) 
* Darell (born 1979) 

